# Style recommendations

## Dictionaries

### Empty dictionary
{}

### Singleline dictionary, inline entries
{k1: a a a a; k2: b; k3: c c c; k4: d d}

### Multiline dictionary, singleline entries
{
  > k1: a a a a
  > k2: b b b
  > k3: c
  > k4: d d
}

### Multiline dictionary, multiline entries
{
  > k1: a a a
    a a a a
  > k2: b b b
  > k3: c c c {
    c c
    c c c c
    c
  }
  > k4: d d d d d
    d d d d d
    d d d d
  > k5: e e e e
    e e e e
  > k6: f f f [
    f f
  ]
}

## Tuples

### Unit tuple
[]

### Singleline tuple, short inline entries
[a|b|c|d|e]

### Singleline tuple, longer inline entries
[a a a | b b b b | c | d d d d d d d | e]

### Multiline tuple, singleline entries
[
  > a a a
  | b b b
  | c c c
]

### Multiline tuple, multiline entries
[
  > [
    a a a
  ]
  | b b
  | c
  | {
    d d d
    d d d d
  }
  | [
    e e
    e e
    e e e
  ]
]

## Lists

### Empty list
[]

### Singleline list, inline entries
[a a a; b b b; c; d; e e]

### Multiline list, inline entries
[
  a a a; b b b; c;
  d; e e; f;
  g g g; h;
]

### Multiline list, singleline entries
[
  > a a a a a a a
  > b
  > c c c c c
  > d d d
]

### Multiline list, multiline entries
[
  > a a a
    a a a a a
  > b b b
  > c c c c {
    c c c c c
  }
  > d d d
    d d
  > [
    e e e
  ]
]

## Tables

### Empty table
[]

### Singleline table, inline rows
[a a|b; c c|d d; e|f f]

### Multiline table, inline rows
[
  a|b|c; d|e|f;
  g|h|i; j|k|l;
]

### Multiline table, singleline rows, short & mostly same width columns
[
  |a|b|c|
  |d|e|f|
  |g|h|i|
]

### Multiline table, singleline rows, longer & mostly same width columns
[
  | a |   b b b| c c |
  | d | e e e e| f f |
  | g | h h h h| i i |
]

### Multiline table, singleline rows, differing width columns
[
  > a a a a a | b | c
  > a a a | b b b b b | c c c c c
  > a | b b | c c
  > a a a a | b b b b b | c c
]

### Multiline table, multiline rows
[
  > a
    a a a
  | b b b b b [
    b b
    b b
  ]
  | c c c c
    c c c

  > d d d d
  | e e e {
    e e
    e e
  }
  | f
]

## Pattern

### Inline pattern within expression
<P>:a:{b b}:c

### Multiline pattern within expression
<P>:a:{b b}:{
  c c c
}

## Expressions

### Inline expression
{a a a{} {c c c} d d d}

### Multiline expression
{
  a a a a {b b b b} c
  c c c [d d d] e e e e
  f f f <g>:h:i:j k k
  k k k k
}

## Constructor notation

### Inline pattern constructor
<P> <> a <> b b <> c

### Multiline pattern constructor
<P> <> a <> b b b b <> [
  c c c c c
]

### Singleline tuple constructor
a a a <> b b <> c c c c c <> d <> e e e

### Multiline tuple constructor
a a a <> {b b b} <> c <> d d <> {
  g g
  g g
  g g g
}
